  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The NCEA can review the quality of ESIAs for (Dutch) investments in risky or politically sensitive situations, where an independent advice is considered of high importance with a view to credibility and reputation management. Preferably this is done at the request of the government concerned, but where necessary, it can also be done at the request of the financing institution.</narrative>
